ğŸ”“ 4ï¸âƒ£ Added Bucket Policy for Public Access
I added this policy to allow public read access:

{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "PublicReadGetObject",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Principal": "*",
      "Action": "s3:GetObject",
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::big-bucket-6-28-25/*"
    }
  ]
}
